<b>Our first crowd-control song! - </b>1/28/01 1:12:12 PM<br>~ <b>Kocho Divah</b><blockquote>As a bard, you'll find yourself pulling for your party. With this song, equipped with your lute, you have a good chance of lulling multiple targets, one at a time, and then pulling just one. Be prepared for resists though! Like all crowd-control-type songs, it is greatly dependent on your charisma.<br><br>Get to know your victims... some are easier to lull than others. If the mob is already aggroed on you, this song won't help you.</blockquote></td></tr></table></blockquote><br><br><br><br><br><br><a href="/songs.asp?&song=8">Back to Normal Mode</a><br><br><br><i>Printed from EQDiva.com on 7/6/03 6:15:31 AM.</i><br><br></td></tr></table>
